# KNOWLEDGE BASE CONTENT (Storage)
# -------------------------
# Do NOT commit the uploaded course files, only the directory structure itself if empty.
# If 'courses/' should only contain user-uploaded content, uncomment the line below.
# If 'courses/' contains initial demo files, keep it commented and ensure git tracking.
# If you want to commit the directory but not its content:
courses/*
!courses/.gitkeep  # Allow committing an empty dir marker

